_sText:
Have you ever wanted to see, how beautiful the water in Counter-Strike: Source can be?
Now you can!

I've created this map, because i was interrested to see the water textures of CS:S!

I'd like to show them to you, too!

There are 20 water textures to see! Some are really beautiful, some others may not be beautiful ;)

There's an AK47 in evere basin!

Hope you like this idea, and have fun watching the pretty water textures! :)

Greetings: Dariouz111
